                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When numerous small items are scattered before the kuchisake-onna, they compulsively begins to count them. The kuchisake-onna becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] to all creatures for [[/br 1d4 #Duration Off-Guard]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
